room_title: Escape room "Special Ops - The Hunt for Kore Anne" by Vincennes Escape Adventures in Vincennes
room_description:
You and your group are an elite intelligence gathering team. You're not the ones putting holes in bad guys, you are the brains of the outfit.
Your mission begins with credible intel on an ALPHA level threat. Somebody or something, code name "Kore Anne", has come into the United States. You and your team are tasked to investigate a lead at a local abandoned warehouse. Everything is routine until everything goes wrong. Your team is captured. Your captors leave grinning, telling you to enjoy what little time you have left. Time is ticking.
